Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Reena Vari was a female Twi'lek Jedi Master and Jedi Consular of the Galactic Republic. During the Battle of Corellia of the Galactic War she was posted at the Shipwright Auxiliary Spaceport in the Blastfield Shipyards, instructing other Consulars.
